CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Dream Finders Homes Inc is engaged in the home building business. It designs, builds, and sells homes in Jacksonville, Orlando, Denver, the Washington D.C. metropolitan area, and Austin. The company operates through six geographical divisions namely, Jacksonville, Orlando, Denver, Washington DC (Capital), and the Carolinas (H&H Homes), Jet Home Loans LLC. Jacksonville division generates most of the revenue for the firm.
